headline: Traders Are Fleeing Stocks Feared to Be Under Threat From AI
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Artificial intelligence’s imprint on US financial markets is unmistakable. Nvidia Corp. is the most valuable company in the world at nearly $4.5 trillion. Startups from OpenAI to Anthropic have raised tens of billions of dollars.
